data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, spacious, and impeccably maintained residence located in a peaceful and family-friendly neighborhood. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home has over 2,600 sqft. It offers comfort, style, and a warm sense of community. It is accentuated by its abundant number of large windows that flood the home’s interior with natural light. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open and an inviting living area, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends. It has a well-equipped kitchen featuring modern appliances, plenty of counter space, and cabinet storage. The master bedroom offers a spacious walk-in closet and an en-suite for ultimate comfort. Three generously sized bedrooms in which the rooms can also serve as home offices, guest rooms, or creative studios, ensuring productivity and inspiration. This home features a partially finished basement. It's a versatile space that can be transformed into a cozy family room, a home gym, or a guest suite, offering endless possibilities for customization. The attached 2-car garage provides secure parking and additional storage space for your convenience.  property is move-in ready with opportunities to personalize it make it your own. Schedule a viewing today and envision yourself living in this delightful home.
